<p>Banks risk averse and NBFC cannot lend cheaply.&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>So, RBI allowed co lending in PSL. Banks can use innovative assessment of creditworthiness by NBFC while banks can provide cheaper loan byco lending</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>NBFC - non traditional use of data, local knowledge , cash flow of the business to determine risk of credit</p>